fields.name: Horizon T101 Folding Treadmill
fields.description: Power your workouts with a 2.5 Continuous-Duty Horsepower motor. The Johnson Drive System helps you stay in perfect rhythm with a durable and responsive drive motor that recalibrate with each footfall so you never feel lags or surges.

fields.name: BH Fitness Pioneer R3 Folding Treadmill
fields.description: A 2.75 CV Motor lets you ramp up your home workouts, hitting top speeds of 18km/h and maximum elevations of 12%. With speed and elevation instant keys, you can switch up these metrics with ease whilst on the run.

fields.name: BH Fitness F2W Dual Treadmill
fields.description: Built for regular home usage, the F2W Dual treadmill from BH Fitness fits and extra-wide running surface into its compact chassis, providing maximum comfort in a minimal space. Hit top speeds of 18 km/h and up to 12 levels of incline, both easily adjustable mid-workout via instant keys, so you don’t have to disrupt your stride.

fields.name: Body Power SP.IC14 Indoor Studio Cycle
fields.description: The Body Power SP.IC14 Indoor Studio Cycle is a stylish studio bike for home use. It comes complete with an easy to read LCD screen, which feeds back time, speed, distance, calories burned and heart rate via the EKG grips.

fields.name: NordicTrack RX800 V1 Folding Rower
fields.description: The Nordic Track RX800 V1 Folding Rowing Machine is a space-saving indoor rower built to provide a full-body cardiovascular workout. Featuring smooth air resistance, this can be easily adjusted to provide the level of intensity you require. Equipped with a comprehensive console, this offers an engaging backlit display and feeds back key workout stats including watts, strokes per minute, total strokes, time and calories.

fields.name: Schwinn 510R Recumbent Cycle
fields.description: Compatible with the Explore the World™ App and Zwift®, you can take a solo adventure across the globe from the comfort of your own home. Explore high-definition locations and interact with others in a virtual world that motivates you at every mile (subscriptions required).

fields.name: ProForm R600 V1 Rower
fields.description: Sleek and stylish, the ProForm R600 V1 Rowing Machine is designed to provide a full-body cardiovascular workout in the comfort of the home setting. Featuring smooth air resistance, this can be easily adjusted to provide the level of intensity you require.

fields.name: Fitness-MAD Hi-Speed 2 way Power Pump
fields.description: 2-way hi-pressure Swiss Ball pump This pump makes blowing up a Swiss ball a breeze with two-way action for faster inflation

fields.name: Body Power 55cm Gym Ball With Pump (300Kg Burst Resistant) Grey
fields.description: Get the ball rolling and achieve easy, convenient core strength and stability exercise – and it’s fun too! The Body Power anti-burst gym ball provides a simple, but effective way to focus on your core strength and stability.

fields.name: Body Power Rubber Hex Dumbbells & Rack 3,4,6,8 & 10Kg
fields.description: This Bodypower dumbbells set includes 5 pairs of hex dumbbells with Body-Solid storage rack. Weights included are one pair each of 3kg, 4kg, 6kg, 8kg and 10kg. These commercial quality Bodypower Hex Dumbbells are a great choice for home or commercial environments.

fields.name: Body Power 1-10Kg Rubber Hex Dumbbell Weight Set
fields.description: 10 pairs in 1kg increments Solid cast dumbbells encased in rubber Protects floors and equipment Reduces noise All steel chrome contoured (ergo) handles - easier and safer to handle Durable rubber will not crack or fade, and prevents damage to floors and equipment Pinned heads for commercial use Unique design ideal for home, vertical and commercial markets

fields.name: Body Power Ultimate Vinyl Coated Kettle Bell & Rack Weight Set
fields.description: Rack included in set. Kettlebell training has taken the fitness world by storm. In just a few years, there are now thousands of people in the United Kingdom that are benefiting from the benefits of kettlebells. In addition, to everyday men and women, many athletes from a variety of sports now use kettlebells in their programs. Kettlebells look like shot putts with a handle and have been used in training the Russian army for centuries. They work a complete range of muscles as you swing the kettlebell backwards and forwards or from side to side. There are cardiovascular benefits also.

fields.name: Body Power Neoprene Kettlebell & Body-Solid Rack Package
fields.description: The Neoprene Covered Kettlebells are built with solid cast iron ensuring maximum durability, whilst the Neoprene coating prevents scratching, splitting and scuffing, both to the floor and the kettlebell. The stylish Body-Solid Kettlebell Rack delivers compact and organised storage for up to 6 kettlebells.

fields.name: Bowflex Stand for SelectTech Barbell and Curl Bar with Media Rack
fields.description: Ergonomically designed, this stand provides a convenient storage solution for your Bowflex SelectTech® Barbell and Curl Bar, protecting your lower back and keeping your workout area tidy.

fields.name: Hammer Strength 10Kg Rubber Straight Barbell
fields.description: Utilising Hammers Strength’s unique X-shaped head design, these fixed barbells are some of the most durable and trusted available to buy. Its anti-roll design makes it ideal from ground-based work, and ensures they won’t roll away when they’re not being used. Durable rubber ensures resistance against scratches and scuffs, and their on-piece structure reduces the noisy clanking you’d usually get from of weight plates during workouts.

fields.name: Life Fitness Activate Series Treadmill
fields.description: Easy to Use The intuitive console design offers exercisers clear and simple direction for quick start or pre-programmed workouts Made to Last Hundreds of hours of testing goes into each and every piece of equipment to ensure its durability and reliability Green to Go Life Fitness is committed to developing products that enable our customers to run greener businesses.

fields.name: Body Power R300 Water Resistance Rower
fields.description: Manufactured from a solid steel frame integrated with a first grade wooden finish, the Body Power R300 really looks (and sounds) the part. Comfort is no issue on the R300. It features a seat that shapes to your form, supporting you throughout every stroke, and thanks to a textured finish, prevents any slipping so you can feel totally secure.

fields.name: York Standard 1" Spring Collars
fields.description:
Great for quick weight plate changes, these spring collars are designed to secure weight plates on standard straight dumbbell bars and barbells.
